name: Maul's Electrobinoculars
Lore: 'Advanced optics used by Darth Maul to help track Queen Amidala. Image enhancement features allow for better sensor readings.',
Text: 'Use 2 Force to deploy on Maul. At any time you may use 1 Force to peek at the top card of your Force Pile. You may move that card to the top of your Reserve Deck.',
